column1: BM | BE: Bugs + New Adjustments - May 09, 2024
column31:
Below are the issues which were Identified during a meeting with [~accountid:63c699e4d16a886a25e60e83] on May 09, 2024



* Head Office: Head office should be just only branch within the complete branch list. Second Headoffice branch cannot be created at any cost
* Branch List: List should show the records order as the last created should be shown on top
* Branch Mapping - Branch Code should be proper - its not creating properly once branch is mapped
* GL Code should be removed from Branch Profile
* Branch Profile - Branch ID should be reflected once the branch Id is generated in branch mapping screen 
* If a branch ID is generated from Branch Profile screen then it should also be reflected on the branch mapping screen

column1: BM | FE: Bugs + New Adjustments - May 09, 2024
column31:
Below are the issues which were Identified during a meeting with [~accountid:63c699e4d16a886a25e60e83] on May 09, 2024

* (label Change) Status - Change to Branch Status (/) 
* (label Change) Branch Status - change to Approval(/) 
* If the user has created the branch then that person should not be allowed to approve any branch. 
* Controls Screen: End Of Day (2nd field in screen) -> Branch Stock Management (Label Change)(/) 
* Branch Profile: Numbers feild shuold not accept characters(/) 
* On Users tab - apply condition: if branch approval status is none then it should not be shown (/) 
* Controls: On new record when a tab is clicked then it throws error even on save  (/) 
* Alerts: Threshold values row add button alignment issue  (/) 
* Threshold: Products: Select All option should be given which should select all the values
* Users: white background should not be stretched to complete page instead it should be filled till the number of rows filled in the grid
* Users UI Issue: Id is left aligned  (/) 
* Threshold: PPC Min Max field condition that max should not be lesser the max field.
* PPC Min Max fields should be moved to Alerts screen
* GL Code should be removed from Branch Profile  (/) 
* Button should be there that can help to Clear filter options
* Area Region + Branch Area MApping: Contxt menu(3 dots) in mapping screen Branch/Area option should be provided. containing options (View and Edit)

column1: Query to  Extract GL Area and Branch Data for MDM Migration
column184:
25/Apr/24 5:03 PM;62df8acbbc2c449f3d93f0e0;Dear [~accountid:60768795c9d3a20072dff7b6] 

We need the query to extracted following Data From GL for migration to MDM Schema.

* *Data Fields:*
*# Area Code
*# Area Name
*# Branch Code
*# Branch Name



cc: 

[~accountid:6391d8c45fc160544e1e0761]
column185:
26/Apr/24 12:18 PM;60768795c9d3a20072dff7b6;Query 1 (Branches only)


{code:sql}-- Value Code Reperesents GL Branch Code, and Value Name is the GL Branch Name.
-- Reference5 Desc denotes whether its a Branch or a Department. (10000 Branch, 20000 Department)
SELECT * FROM CORE.COR_SEGMENT_VALUE WHERE VALUE_LEVEL_HIDDEN_VALUE  LIKE 'BRANCH_CODE';{code}

Query 2 (Branch Area)


{code:sql}-- Here value code reperesents the starting code of every branch 
-- and value name being the name of branch area
-- e.g. if its 8, then its UAE based branches e.g. 8001 head office.
-- 8 being branch area and 001 being the branch code digits.
SELECT * FROM CORE.COR_SEGMENT_VALUE WHERE VALUE_LEVEL_HIDDEN_VALUE LIKE 'BRANCH_AREA';{code}

Query 3 (with joins for each branch name along with its branch area value)

{code:sql}SELECT b.VALUE_CODE AS BRANCH_CODE, b.VALUE_NAME AS BRANCH_NAME, ba.VALUE_CODE AS BRANCH_AREA_CODE, ba.VALUE_NAME AS BRANCH_AREA_NAME
FROM CORE.COR_SEGMENT_VALUE b
INNER JOIN CORE.COR_SEGMENT_VALUE ba ON b.PARENT_VALUE_CODE = ba.VALUE_CODE AND ba.VALUE_LEVEL_HIDDEN_VALUE = 'BRANCH_AREA'
WHERE b.VALUE_LEVEL_HIDDEN_VALUE LIKE 'BRANCH_CODE';{code}
